      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PYEKAKARIKI (8) settled in front and kept going to record a emphatic 9 metres win last start over 1770m at this track, following on from a strong second the run prior at this track. Should enjoy a nice smother from this draw and will be looking for a split at some stage. Tackles a similar assignment and he can salute once again. LETSGO MATILDA (7) did a good job to finish third two starts ago then registered an effortless win last start, scoring by 6 metres over 1760m at Junee. Gets a soft run on the inside of the second line but may need luck at some point. Tackles a similar assignment and she can go right on with the job. MICTON MOUSE (5) led from one spot wider when placed last start ay Goulburn and owns a good record at this circuit and distance. LETSTACOBOUTIT (9) has won his past two starts, the latest at Temora a week ago. Difficult to ignore that sort of form.",
